attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Classic Realty NW - Ely

data.description: Spacious 3-bedroom ranch home on Ely’s east end. Home features a foyer entrance to the kitchen with custom cabinetry, newer range/oven, and island separation to the dining room. Cozy living room with many built-ins and 3 nicely sized bedrooms. Both baths have been partially updated with tile and fixtures. Amazing bonus room on the main finished with tongue & groove, propane fireplace, and adds main floor laundry to complete this well thought out floor plan. Full unfinished basement with an electric sauna and ample storage. This nicely treed corner lot boasts beautiful perennial gardens, patio, and a detached 2-car garage.
